  "texts": [
    "Additionally, the reporter specified the property of the bug, such as the product and component containing the bug.",
    "After the submission, other participants contributed comments in the comment field.",
    "The bug report and its associated comments are typically utilized by software developers to facilitate subsequent software activities.The general activities to manage bug reports for bug fixing involve six steps [634] (as shown in Figure 6).",
    "Upon the submission of a new bug report, its initial status is labeled as new.",
    "Subsequently, the bug report undergoes manual scrutiny to verify its validity and prevent duplication."
